Silk Romance Halter Dress. A stunning full length bridesmaid dress by designer Tania Olsen. A flattering halterneck style featuring a ruched bodice and beaded neckline. Available in Champagne & Peacock.

Lace Full Length Bridesmaid Dress. A gorgeous full length crinkle chiffon dress with a sleeveless lace bodice. All dresses are made to order especially for you and will be shipped from the USA.

Audrina Dress. Stunning A-lined maxi dress with embellishment for your bridesmaids. Features gathering to accentuate and minimalise the waist. Fully lined. Available in lilac, blosson pink and ivory.

Plume Silk Maxi Dress by Truese. The Plume Maxi Dress is a stunning full length dress by Australian designer Truese. Features a high neckline with beaded detail on the bodice. Available in Ink & White.
Gwyneth dress by Pia Gladys Perey. Glamorous draped gown by Pia Gladys Perey. Plunging neckline with draped detailing at the waist. Available in Cadette Blue and available in Custom Colours.

Long Formal White Gown - Beach Wedding Dress - Kylie Dress by Pia Gladys Perey. Stunning keyhole neckline draped dress by designer Pia Gladys Perey. Features luxurious silky jersey draping and a split up the front centre. Custom colour your own dress in one of our numerous colour options

Dessy Britney Strapless Chiffon Dress. A gorgeous full length strapless dress by Dessy Collections. Featuring a flowing drape detail from the sweetheart neckline and a front centre slit. All dresses are made to order especially for you and will be shipped from the USA.

Dessy Cheri One Shoulder Dress. A stunning full length one shoulder gown by Dessy Collections. Features an off the shoulder drape detail and pleated skirt. A gorgeous full length strapless dress by Dessy Collections. Featuring a flowing drape detail from the sweetheart neckline and a front centre slit.

Ingrid Dress by PGP. One shoulder draped dress with elastic stretch waist and a wrap style skirt that drapes and splits when you walk. A very flattering style available in Rust and can be Custom Coloured in a colour of your choice.

Bella Maxi by Truese. A stunning floor sweeping gown by Truese. A timeless strapless style with ruching on the bust that flatters many different shapes and sizes. Available in Black, Champagne, Cameo & Midnight.

Convertible Multi-Wear Bridesmaid Dresses by Goddess By Nature. The perfect convertible dress - one style can be worn in over 30 ways. Colour swatches can be requested here or you can place an order for a Sample - once the sample is returned you will be offered a full refund or credit.
Madeline Dress by Pia Gladys Perey. Gorgeous full length jersey gown with gathered details on the straps and waist and a beautiful cowl-neck back. Available in Latte and numerous Custom Colours.
Anna Dress. A gorgeoud cocktail length dress. Featuring a surplice ruched bodice, sheer cape shoulders and lace overlay skirt.
Kristina Dress. An elegant cocktail length dress, perfect for your bridesmaids. Featuring a draped one shoulder and waistband with beaded accent. Available in Blue Willow & Coffee.
Bianca Dress By Pia Gladys Perey. Very easy, loose fit V-neck maxi. Features crossover pieces of fabric which drapes down the middle. Ties together inside. Made from luxurious, stretch jersey.
Pure Essence Maxi. Stunning 100% silk maxi dress by Honey & Beau. Opens up at the front with a low leg slit.

Kresta Dress By PGP. Beautifully gathered v-neck full length gown. Lots of fabric with draping detail. Stretch jersey material to enable an easy fit - pull on, pull off dress with no zips. Slight train on the back of dress.
Fallon Dress by Pia Gladys Perey. A gorgeous V-neck cocktail dress by Pia Gladys Perey. An elegant style featuring a peplum at the waist.
One Shoulder Jersey Bridesmaid Dress. An elegant midi-length dress by Pia Gladys Perey. A one shoulder dress featuring draped detailing through the dress and a subtle side leg split.
Shellie Chiffon Cocktail Dress. A stunning cocktail dress. A high neckline style featuring vertical ruching on the bust and an embellished belt. Available in Blush, Floss & Lemon.
Hepburn Dress by Jadore. Channel Katharine Hepburn in this stunning dress in a classic cut.
Cocktail Draped Evening Dress. A flattering cocktail dress with a keyhole neckline and gathered skirt. Available in Lime and numerous Custom Colours.
